This package was extracted from the RoboScope project
(https://github.com/viadee/roboscope) so it can be installed
standalone via PyPI by Robot Framework users who want self-healing
selectors without taking on the rest of the RoboScope stack.

The source originated as the `backend/src/recording/heal/` module of
RoboScope (story SH-2, expanded by SH-3 / SH-4 / SH-5). All commits
prior to this package's first tag live in the RoboScope repository.
